ReleaseYear: Year in which the token was released
WhitepaperURL: URL at which the whitepaper of the token whitepaper is available at
RegulatoryFramework: Name of the regulatory framework under which the token is issued
MiCA.IsCompliant: True if the token is MiCA compliant
MiCA.TokenType: Description of how the issuer's tokens are regulated under MiCA (e.g. ART or EMT)
